- **Packages**: `hyperref` is included to enable hyperlinks in the table of contents.
- **Sections**: The document is divided into sections and subsections using `\section` and `\subsection` commands.
- **Table of Contents**: The `\tableofcontents` command is placed after the title and before the main content to generate the table of contents.

This LaTeX document structure will automatically generate a table of contents that reflects the hierarchical structure of the sections and subsections.

